{
  "texts": [
    "Fine-tuning a model as extensive as LLaMA-3 8B required significant computational resources.",
    "This dependency on highend resources limits the accessibility of our approach for researchers with constrained computational capacities.",
    "Furthermore, the models were trained and evaluated on the DAIR-AI Emotion and SWMH datasets, which, while diverse, may not fully capture the complexity and variability of real-world psychological text data.",
    "This could restrict the generalizability of the findings to other domains, languages, or text formats, e.g., short vs. long text.",
    "Additionally, our study does not address the practical integration of these tools into clinical workflows, which would require collaboration with domain experts and rigorous validation."
  ]
}